====USage notes====
* Since ''copa'' is feminine but ''campeonato'' is masculine, as a noun, '''mundial''' can be treated both as a feminine or a masculine noun, depending on the person who says or the region (in Mexico is masculine, for ex. they say ''voy a ver el mundial'', = "I am going to watch one or more FIFA World Cup matches").
